    About this hotel

    This upscale beachfront hotel on the Bay of Tangier is 6 km from both Kasbah Museum and Dar-el-Makhzen, a former Sultan's palace.

    Beachcomber-chic rooms feature free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and minibars. They also come with balconies or terraces overlooking the gardens and/or the sea. Refined suites add separate living rooms, and some have dining rooms. A massive top-tier suite has a private nightclub.

    Free buffet-style breakfast is served in a Swiss-influenced restaurant with a summer terrace; an ornate second restaurant offers Moroccan fare. There's also a lobby bar, a gym and a casino, plus an outdoor pool and gardens.

    Check-in time: 2:00 PM
    Check-out time: 12:00 PM
